node.text: #NYFW 21 @prettylittlething @teyanataylor well done everyone what a show 👏🏽👏🏽👏🏽

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Umar Kamani on September 10, 2021 tagging @teyanataylor, and @prettylittlething. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: WOW!!! Take a bow @teyanataylor you and the entire team smashed it last night for #nyfw @prettylittlething catwalk show, the collection was on point. Models were diverse, show was inclusive and looked a whole vibe. Thank you and well done to everyone involved, we keep it moving and focus on the next steps now.. back to business.. constantly evolving this brand is what makes it most fun! Thanks to everyone who stepped out to support and to everyone who supported online.. 🙏🏽🦄🌎 this is your brand @prettylittlething
